https://assets-v2.lottiefiles.com/a/359d.description:
Lottie animations are a popular choice in website design to enhance user experience and engagement. Lottie is an open-source animation file format that allows designers to export animations from Adobe After Effects and use them on the web seamlessly. These animations are lightweight, scalable, and highly customizable, making them ideal for enhancing the visual appeal of websites.

By incorporating Lottie animations into a website design, you can bring static elements to life, create interactive and dynamic interfaces, and convey information more engagingly. Whether it's subtle micro-interactions, loading animations, or complex visual narratives, Lottie animations add a layer of sophistication and creativity to the overall user interface.

The "Page Not Found 404" error message is a standard response code indicating that the server could not find the requested webpage. It typically appears when users attempt to access a URL that doesn't exist or has been moved or deleted. The "404" code is part of the Hypertext Transfer Protocol (HTTP) status codes, and it's accompanied by a message such as "Page Not Found" or "404 Error."

This error message serves to inform users that the webpage they are trying to access is unavailable, helping them understand why they couldn't reach their intended destination. Website administrators often customize the 404 error page to provide helpful information, such as suggesting navigation options, offering a search bar, or providing links to popular pages, to guide users back to the desired content.

Symbolism: The Black target with a white center represents the company's commitment to hitting the mark when it comes to meeting customer needs and expectations. its indicate the circular animation motion often associated with energy, passion, and action, while the white center provides a sense of balance and clarity.
Usage: The Target logo is prominently displayed on the company's stores, website, advertising materials, and products. It serves as a strong brand identifier and plays a crucial role in the company's marketing efforts.
